#: templates/landing/index.html:8
msgid "Welcome to Open Congress"
msgstr "Bienvenido a Open Congress"

#: templates/landing/index.html:11
msgid ""
"Open Congress brings together public information from the Peruvian "
"Congress in one place. Explore bills from the 2021-2026 congressional "
"period, review who authored them, see how congress members voted, and "
"compare changes between different versions of each bill."
msgstr ""
"Open Congress reune informacion publica del Congreso peruano en un solo "
"lugar. Explora proyectos de ley del periodo congresal 2021-2026, revisa "
"quienes los presentaron, observa como votaron los congresistas y compara "
"cambios entre distintas versiones de cada proyecto."

#: templates/landing/index.html:12
msgid "Click below to start exploring:"
msgstr "Haz clic abajo para empezar a explorar:"

#: templates/landing/index.html:31
msgid "Open Congress logo"
msgstr "Logo de Open Congress"

#: templates/landing/index.html:33
msgid "Transparency and accountability for a stronger democracy"
msgstr "Transparencia y rendicion de cuentas para una democracia mas fuerte"

#: templates/landing/index.html:47
msgid ""
"Open Congress is built as a public data pipeline for legislative "
"information. It collects official public records from the Peruvian "
"Congress, processes them, and organizes them into a structured, clean "
"relational database."
msgstr ""
"Open Congress esta construido como un pipeline publico de datos para "
"informacion legislativa. Recopila registros publicos oficiales del "
"Congreso peruano, los procesa y los organiza en una base de datos "
"relacional estructurada y limpia."

#: templates/landing/index.html:48
msgid ""
"The platform began as part of the University of Chicago's Master of "
"Computational Analysis and Public Policy program and is developed by a "
"six-student team from the program."
msgstr ""
"La plataforma nacio como parte del programa Master of Computational "
"Analysis and Public Policy de la Universidad de Chicago y es desarrollada"
" por un equipo de seis estudiantes del programa."

#: templates/landing/index.html:49
msgid ""
"It is mainly written in Python and uses SQLAlchemy, SQLite, OCR/document "
"parsing, and automated tests to track bills, votes, congressmembers, "
"political groups, and text changes across the legislative process."
msgstr ""
"Esta escrita principalmente en Python y usa SQLAlchemy, SQLite, "
"OCR/procesamiento de documentos y pruebas automatizadas para seguir "
"proyectos de ley, votos, congresistas, grupos politicos y cambios de "
"texto a lo largo del proceso legislativo."

